{"tid":1870234,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"支持武漢！ 國米在米蘭打比中身穿印有中國加油的球衣比賽","createTime":"2020-02-08T16:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T07:05:22.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0f07dd563e8b859068106679b3742deb0268ed88","tid":1870234,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LXTAiqC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLXTAiqC.png&h=5565a478&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"466a0eb35738b4ac07286861ab7a0ef6c498cdd7","tid":1870234,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"另外，國米方面還表示，&ldquo;始終不渝，團結如一，武漢加油&rdquo;這句話也將出現在梅阿查球場的各個區域。<br />\n<br />\n 中國的新型肺炎疫情也牽動著國米上下人員的心，俱樂部此前向武漢捐贈了30萬隻口罩，全力支持抗疫行動。"},{"pid":"52f74d3a4573ea103afb695a9fbe7d8f1487962e","tid":1870234,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"香港反朗仲支持國米奪冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d009cac36279bb751e358decbcbbeb62a8577a3","tid":1870234,"uid":12628,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"我支持蛆再冧莊意甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a43e90b84b4932bc03974801c1b587cabe620de","tid":1870234,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d009cac36279bb751e358decbcbbeb62a8577a3","tid":1870234,"uid":12628,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"我支持蛆再冧莊意甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"可以做朗迷了"},{"pid":"02364abae3de016736916b4a1f0d59ec468f76d0","tid":1870234,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"此外，國際米蘭球會官方宣佈，將在米蘭打吡期間，繼續為武漢、為中國加油。國際米蘭的官方公告如下：「在新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情發生後，值此艱難時刻，國際米蘭向武漢及全體中國人民送出祝福我們與你們同在，挺住！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  「香港時間2月10日淩晨進行的米蘭打吡中，國際米蘭將身穿印有『中國加油』主題臂章的波衫進行比賽。『始終不渝，團結如一。武漢加油』，這句話也將出現在梅阿查球場的各個區域。在過去的幾天裡，球會主席張康陽和國際米蘭向武漢捐贈了30萬隻醫用口罩，而蘇寧集團自疫情發生後就一直為抗疫行動，包括提供免費航運服務，並向醫院和當地機構捐贈國外進口的產品。」"},{"pid":"40eb05c4354d558a2dac57dc3c4c13ce38bddd36","tid":1870234,"uid":55854,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:11:18.000Z","msg":"去武漢踢返場友誼賽囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d904141509689dcf646eca3703230e3c9def7123","tid":1870234,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:19:03.000Z","msg":"P4武漢"},{"pid":"0306ce7eaadc7279acd3c4ec0aff16fb9827b6d6","tid":1870234,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"中國肺炎加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0704372cc2e656f9b7a167414c4218eb7ce8f145","tid":1870234,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0306ce7eaadc7279acd3c4ec0aff16fb9827b6d6","tid":1870234,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"中國肺炎加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4484ce5bdace1e8314863b31c47a49c775a79b7a","tid":1870234,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d009cac36279bb751e358decbcbbeb62a8577a3","tid":1870234,"uid":12628,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"我支持蛆再冧莊意甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"我支持拉齊奧"},{"pid":"c7059975773e63117d6572d769285803e8bd0463","tid":1870234,"uid":64026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d009cac36279bb751e358decbcbbeb62a8577a3","tid":1870234,"uid":12628,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"cited